418350,"uid":31151,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:35:45.000Z","msg":"班速龍係威係勢又裝甲車咁 屌咪又係黎拆路障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d895a484e85419229db9307a51afd7550f8d0ea3","tid":1418350,"uid":293261,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:36:13.000Z","msg":"班警狗喺度做乜9 <br />\n嘈撚住晒 屌佢老母"},{"pid":"b5f04ce234dba4188de3a9b3af3e4c5e5797cb0e","tid":1418350,"uid":222451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:36:15.000Z","msg":"勇武盡失民心 全港唔支持 運動即將玩完!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418149\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418149</a><br />\n<br />\n互推!"},{"pid":"44f7f3e6179b5cf5d4606af6e4efa578ae282e18","tid":1418350,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:36:31.000Z","msg":"一早要出啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce2f24cfbcf31bc7d1fcb333c154a9c9932fc25c","tid":1418350,"uid":189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:36:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Hong_Kong_Police_Unimog_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FFile%3AHong_Kong_Police_Unimog_1.jpg&h=7fe8705e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2008年12月，警務處引進的6輛平治烏尼莫U5000（官方稱為銳武）裝甲車逐步運抵香港，經過測試及改裝後，於翌年3月投入服務。新裝甲車由德國製造裝甲車身及其環境保護柴油引擎，由法國製造軍警專用四輪驅動底盤，行駛速度比較舊款裝甲車輛快速，而且防彈性能更佳[45][46][47][48]，每輛價值600萬港元[49][50][51][52]，每輛可以運載包括駕駛員在內共10名人員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/香港警察車輛\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E8%BB%8A%E8%BC%9B&d=bDHmYwogulq9FkNLxWxOtlznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=ddf5db9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/香港警察車輛</a><br />\n<br />\n似係呢款？都成十年貨仔"},{"pid":"a82e10431940ec680a31cf5e41d615db2c1e550e","tid":1418350,"uid":31151,"like":0,"