8%BB%8A%E8%BC%9B&d=bDHmYwogulq9FkNLxWxOtlznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=ddf5db9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/香港警察車輛</a><br />\n<br />\n似係呢款？都成十年貨仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:38:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/1/14/Hong_Kong_Police_Unimog_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F1%2F14%2FHong_Kong_Police_Unimog_1.jpg&h=8fc3eb31&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"164df55e0a2cf1172cd5ec964dd2c43ab02fcc6e","tid":1418350,"uid":259613,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:38:25.000Z","msg":"五大訴求<br />\n1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n4.追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n兄弟爬山 各有各做<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"2b2c4d75dcb07c9b134ea414a1e05efca6010c5f","tid":1418350,"uid":259613,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:38:49.000Z","msg":"咁我地真係要出雞尾酒"},{"pid":"6cd221e6b0f7577ce1678bee2b4634585df25f92","tid":1418350,"uid":293261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:40:40.000Z","msg":"班死差佬日日屈人<br />\n必遭天譴"},{"pid":"245b84fba1ee204e670b5e6b23848f97a130ef1b","tid":1418350,"uid":206080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f525cbd7cc6f4b15d92456907f340787eb42e593","tid":1418350,"uid":286131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:33:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解警狗甘有錢買gear對付自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:43:04.000Z","msg":"除咗有貪污，諗唔到有其他可能性"},{"pid":"0810bbc4862949e571dde161adfca89b5c9b4d2c","tid":1418350,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbf912ec17